# React Patterns

- Functional components only. Named exports for shared components; default export only for pages.
- Extract reusable logic into hooks (`useX`). Page orchestration hooks live in the feature.
- `useState` for local UI state in a single component. Cross-component UI state → Effect Atom.
- Server/async data → TanStack Query via `queryOptions()` in `*.queries.ts` (Effects in `queryFn`).
- Atoms: `useAtomValue(atom)` / `useAtomSet(atom)` to limit re-renders.
- Wrap the app with `RegistryProvider` (see `@app/providers`).
- Follow React Compiler rules — ESLint enforces them.
